<p>Read the <a href="https://epochai.org/assets/docs/Epoch%20Impact%20Report%20-%202022.pdf" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">full report</a> to learn about <a href="https://epochai.org/assets/docs/Epoch%20Impact%20Report%20-%202022.pdf#page=4" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">our key insights this year</a>, an overview of our <a href="https://epochai.org/assets/docs/Epoch%20Impact%20Report%20-%202022.pdf#page=10" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">research</a> and <a href="https://epochai.org/assets/docs/Epoch%20Impact%20Report%20-%202022.pdf#page=12" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">non-research activities</a>, and our <a href="https://epochai.org/assets/docs/Epoch%20Impact%20Report%20-%202022.pdf#page=15" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">plans for the future</a>.</p>




